content: Premium rates with GST for aged fifty and below for twenty six months policy are five hundred seven dollars for Basic plan, five hundred fifty six dollars and ninety cents for Enhanced plan, five hundred eighty three dollars and sixty cents for Premier plan, and six hundred ninety two dollars for Exclusive plan.
